title: goblin_cantina_chieftain
---
Fretjaw: Mind the tables, friend. We don't FIGHT in the cantina, we REHEARSE fighting. There's a difference. Mostly the volume.
-> What goes on here?
    <<jump goblin_cantina_chieftain__1>>
-> Why a training pit, not a stronghold?
    <<jump goblin_cantina_chieftain__2>>
-> Walk away.
    Fretjaw bangs a flagon on the dais. The entire pit cheers, then immediately resumes losing at darts.
===

title: goblin_cantina_chieftain__1
---
Fretjaw: House rules: vault the tables, duck the bar shelf, buy a round if you bleed on the floorboards. Three goblins are passed out under the dais. They are also house rules.
-> Ask another question.
    <<jump goblin_cantina_chieftain__0>>
-> Walk away.
    Fretjaw bangs a flagon on the dais. The cheering is real. The dart skill is not.
===

title: goblin_cantina_chieftain__2
---
Fretjaw: Strongholds make you proud. Pits make you GOOD. Anyone can stand a wall up. Try keeping your footing on a beer floor.
-> Ask another question.
    <<jump goblin_cantina_chieftain__0>>
-> Walk away.
    Fretjaw bangs a flagon on the dais. The cheering is real. The dart skill is not.
===

title: military_general
---
General: AT EASE, RECRUIT. You have ascended the Tower of Acceptable Casualties. Below us: parade grounds. Above us: bureaucracy. Around us: an oath you have not yet sworn.
-> What is this place?
    <<jump military_general__1>>
-> Why so many medals?
    <<jump military_general__2>>
-> Salute and withdraw.
    The General returns the salute with surgical precision and twelve audible clicks.
===

title: military_general__1
---
General: This is the Iron Bastion of the Faction Of Steel — a tower built from after-action reports and hand-cranked optimism. We host parades on the parts that aren't structural.
-> Ask another question.
    <<jump military_general__0>>
-> Salute and withdraw.
    The General returns the salute with surgical precision and twelve audible clicks.
===

title: military_general__2
---
General: Each medal commemorates a meeting I survived. Three are for punctuality. Two are for the meetings ABOUT punctuality. The largest one is awarded by, and to, myself.
-> Ask another question.
    <<jump military_general__0>>
-> Salute and withdraw.
    The General returns the salute with surgical precision and twelve audible clicks.
===

title: pulse_voyager_captain
---
Captain Pulse: Welcome aboard the dais, drifter. We don't moor in the sky because we LIKE heights. We moor here because the tide is a measurement, not a condition.
-> Where do these stones lead?
    <<jump pulse_voyager_captain__1>>
-> Why park up in the sky?
    <<jump pulse_voyager_captain__2>>
-> Cast off.
    Captain Pulse touches a rune on the dais. The stones below shimmer once, as if amused, and stay put.
===

title: pulse_voyager_captain__1
---
Captain Pulse: Each stone is a beat. Skip one and you don't fall — you just arrive late. Late is a kind of wrong place that pretends to be a wrong time.
-> Ask another question.
    <<jump pulse_voyager_captain__0>>
-> Cast off.
    Captain Pulse offers a salute that ends in a wave. Or a wave that ends in a salute. Hard to tell.
===

title: pulse_voyager_captain__2
---
Captain Pulse: Below the stones is water. Above them is also water, just slower. We split the difference and call the difference a deck.
-> Ask another question.
    <<jump pulse_voyager_captain__0>>
-> Cast off.
    Captain Pulse offers a salute that ends in a wave. Or a wave that ends in a salute. Hard to tell.
===

title: tech_bros_disruptor
---
Chadwick III: Welcome to the basement! We're not failing — we're SUBTERRANEAN. Premium iteration depth. We dropped down here on purpose; gravity is just runway you don't have to lobby for.
-> What is this place pivoting toward?
    <<jump tech_bros_disruptor__1>>
-> Why does the boardroom face up?
    <<jump tech_bros_disruptor__2>>
-> Touch grass.
    Chadwick blinks. \"You'll be back. The runway always slopes downward.\"
===

title: tech_bros_disruptor__1
---
Chadwick III: Disruption-as-a-service, friend. We disrupt anything that holds still long enough. Our roadmap is a slope. Our slope is the roadmap. Both are pivots.
-> Ask another question.
    <<jump tech_bros_disruptor__0>>
-> Touch grass.
    Chadwick uploads the conversation to a deck and shareholders applaud somewhere far away.
===

title: tech_bros_disruptor__2
---
Chadwick III: The boardroom faces up because vision is a direction. Looking down is for accountants. We do not look down. We are the down.
-> Ask another question.
    <<jump tech_bros_disruptor__0>>
-> Touch grass.
    Chadwick uploads the conversation to a deck and shareholders applaud somewhere far away.
